
Things I had to do (In no particular order)
--------------------------------------------
1) setup SSL
2) setup SSH
3) git clone Repos (app folders)
4) git clone base-server-install

5) configured ACL via /etc/fstab
        What I did:
        ------------------------------------
        /home    ext4   defaults,acl   0   2
        sudo mount -o remount /

6)  Reset some permissions:
    --------------------------
    sudo chown -R www-data:webdev /var/www
    sudo chmod -R ug=wrx,o= /var/www
